{
  "video_id": "2UxGrde1NDA",
  "title": "Heather Barnett: What humans can learn from semi-intelligent slime",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12632.0,
      "end_time": 15737.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to introduce you to an organism:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15737.0,
      "end_time": 19193.0,
      "text": "a slime mold, Physarum polycephalum."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19193.0,
      "end_time": 22150.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a mold with an identity crisis, because it&#39;s not a mold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22150.0,
      "end_time": 23945.0,
      "text": "so let&#39;s get that straight to start with."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23945.0,
      "end_time": 26481.0,
      "text": "It is one of 700 known slime molds"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26481.0,
      "end_time": 28618.0,
      "text": "belonging to the kingdom of the amoeba."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28618.0,
      "end_time": 31241.0,
      "text": "It is a single-celled organism, a cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31241.0,
      "end_time": 33481.0,
      "text": "that joins together with other cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33481.0,
      "end_time": 35713.0,
      "text": "to form a mass super-cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35713.0,
      "end_time": 37953.0,
      "text": "to maximize its resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37953.0,
      "end_time": 40113.0,
      "text": "So within a slime mold you might find thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40113.0,
      "end_time": 42360.0,
      "text": "or millions of nuclei,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42360.0,
      "end_time": 44121.0,
      "text": "all sharing a cell wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44121.0,
      "end_time": 47229.0,
      "text": "all operating as one entity."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47229.0,
      "end_time": 48833.0,
      "text": "In its natural habitat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48833.0,
      "end_time": 51629.0,
      "text": "you might find the slime mold foraging in woodlands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51629.0,
      "end_time": 55330.0,
      "text": "eating rotting vegetation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55330.0,
      "end_time": 56870.0,
      "text": "but you might equally find it"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56870.0,
      "end_time": 58412.0,
      "text": "in research laboratories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58412.0,
      "end_time": 62614.0,
      "text": "classrooms, and even artists&#39; studios."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62614.0,
      "end_time": 65548.0,
      "text": "I first came across the slime mold about five years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65549.0,
      "end_time": 67106.0,
      "text": "A microbiologist friend of mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67106.0,
      "end_time": 70229.0,
      "text": "gave me a petri dish with a little yellow blob in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70230.0,
      "end_time": 73238.0,
      "text": "and told me to go home and play with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73238.0,
      "end_time": 75245.0,
      "text": "The only instructions I was given,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75245.0,
      "end_time": 77290.0,
      "text": "that it likes it dark and damp"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77290.0,
      "end_time": 81360.0,
      "text": "and its favorite food is porridge oats."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81360.0,
      "end_time": 83378.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an artist who&#39;s worked for many years"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83378.0,
      "end_time": 86225.0,
      "text": "with biology, with scientific processes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86225.0,
      "end_time": 89235.0,
      "text": "so living material is not uncommon for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89236.0,
      "end_time": 91341.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve worked with plants, bacteria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 91341.0,
      "end_time": 92860.0,
      "text": "cuttlefish, fruit flies."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92860.0,
      "end_time": 95462.0,
      "text": "So I was keen to get my new collaborator home"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95462.0,
      "end_time": 96838.0,
      "text": "to see what it could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 96838.0,
      "end_time": 100390.0,
      "text": "So I took it home and I watched."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100400.0,
      "end_time": 102810.0,
      "text": "I fed it a varied diet."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102810.0,
      "end_time": 104734.0,
      "text": "I observed as it networked."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104734.0,
      "end_time": 107900.0,
      "text": "It formed a connection between food sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107100.0,
      "end_time": 109848.0,
      "text": "I watched it leave a trail behind it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109848.0,
      "end_time": 111607.0,
      "text": "indicating where it had been."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111607.0,
      "end_time": 114554.0,
      "text": "And I noticed that when it was fed up with one petri dish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114555.0,
      "end_time": 117534.0,
      "text": "it would escape and find a better home."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117534.0,
      "end_time": 119262.0,
      "text": "I captured my observations"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119262.0,
      "end_time": 121220.0,
      "text": "through time-lapse photography."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 121220.0,
      "end_time": 123860.0,
      "text": "Slime mold grows at about one centimeter an hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123860.0,
      "end_time": 126441.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s not really ideal for live viewing"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126441.0,
      "end_time": 129294.0,
      "text": "unless there&#39;s some form of really extreme meditation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129294.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131822.0,
      "text": "but through the time lapse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131822.0,
      "end_time": 134918.0,
      "text": "I could observe some really interesting behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134918.0,
      "end_time": 138418.0,
      "text": "For instance, having fed on a nice pile of oats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 138418.0,
      "end_time": 142862.0,
      "text": "the slime mold goes off to explore new territories"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 142862.0,
      "end_time": 145594.0,
      "text": "in different directions simultaneously."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 145594.0,
      "end_time": 147833.0,
      "text": "When it meets itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147833.0,
      "end_time": 149700.0,
      "text": "it knows it&#39;s already there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 149700.0,
      "end_time": 151654.0,
      "text": "it recognizes it&#39;s there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 151654.0,
      "end_time": 153201.0,
      "text": "and instead retreats back"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 153201.0,
      "end_time": 156881.0,
      "text": "and grows in other directions."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 156881.0,
      "end_time": 159205.0,
      "text": "I was quite impressed by this feat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 159205.0,
      "end_time": 162755.0,
      "text": "at how what was essentially just a bag of cellular slime"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 162755.0,
      "end_time": 165984.0,
      "text": "could somehow map its territory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165985.0,
      "end_time": 169457.0,
      "text": "know itself, and move with seeming intention."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 169457.0,
      "end_time": 173109.0,
      "text": "I found countless scientific studies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 173110.0,
      "end_time": 175155.0,
      "text": "research papers, journal articles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 175155.0,
      "end_time": 179379.0,
      "text": "all citing incredible work with this one organism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 179379.0,
      "end_time": 181343.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to share a few of those with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 181343.0,
      "end_time": 184303.0,
      "text": "For example, a team in Hokkaido University in Japan"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 184303.0,
      "end_time": 186335.0,
      "text": "filled a maze with slime mold."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 186335.0,
      "end_time": 188431.0,
      "text": "It joined together and formed a mass cell."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 188431.0,
      "end_time": 190783.0,
      "text": "They introduced food at two points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 190783.0,
      "end_time": 191981.0,
      "text": "oats of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 191981.0,
      "end_time": 193626.0,
      "text": "and it formed a connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 193627.0,
      "end_time": 195410.0,
      "text": "between the food."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 195410.0,
      "end_time": 197525.0,
      "text": "It retracted from empty areas and dead ends."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197525.0,
      "end_time": 200335.0,
      "text": "There are four possible routes through this maze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 200335.0,
      "end_time": 202440.0,
      "text": "yet time and time again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 202440.0,
      "end_time": 204607.0,
      "text": "the slime mold established the shortest"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 204607.0,
      "end_time": 207600.0,
      "text": "and the most efficient route."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207600.0,
      "end_time": 208311.0,
      "text": "Quite clever."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 208311.0,
      "end_time": 210500.0,
      "text": "The conclusion from their experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 210500.0,
      "end_time": 213470.0,
      "text": "was that the slime mold had a primitive form of intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 213470.0,
      "end_time": 216910.0,
      "text": "Another study exposed cold air at regular intervals to the slime mold."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 216910.0,
      "end_time": 219255.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t like it. It doesn&#39;t like it cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 219255.0,
      "end_time": 220448.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t like it dry."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 220448.0,
      "end_time": 222563.0,
      "text": "They did this at repeat intervals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 222563.0,
      "end_time": 224220.0,
      "text": "and each time, the slime mold"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 224221.0,
      "end_time": 227351.0,
      "text": "slowed down its growth in response."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 227351.0,
      "end_time": 229195.0,
      "text": "However, at the next interval,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 229195.0,
      "end_time": 232190.0,
      "text": "the researchers didn&#39;t put the cold air on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 232190.0,
      "end_time": 235313.0,
      "text": "yet the slime mold slowed down in anticipation"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 235313.0,
      "end_time": 236649.0,
      "text": "of it happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 236649.0,
      "end_time": 239175.0,
      "text": "It somehow knew that it was about the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 239175.0,
      "end_time": 241131.0,
      "text": "for the cold air that it didn&#39;t like."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 241131.0,
      "end_time": 242820.0,
      "text": "The conclusion from their experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242820.0,
      "end_time": 246900.0,
      "text": "was that the slime mold was able to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 246900.0,
      "end_time": 247321.0,
      "text": "A third experiment:"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 247321.0,
      "end_time": 249880.0,
      "text": "the slime mold was invited"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249880.0,
      "end_time": 253280.0,
      "text": "to explore a territory covered in oats."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253280.0,
      "end_time": 256327.0,
      "text": "It fans out in a branching pattern."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 256327.0,
      "end_time": 258975.0,
      "text": "As it goes, each food node it finds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 258975.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261675.00000000003,
      "text": "it forms a network, a connection to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 261675.0,
      "end_time": 263423.0,
      "text": "and keeps foraging."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 263423.0,
      "end_time": 265864.0,
      "text": "After 26 hours, it established"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 265864.0,
      "end_time": 267481.0,
      "text": "quite a firm network"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 267481.0,
      "end_time": 269271.0,
      "text": "between the different oats."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 269271.0,
      "end_time": 271910.0,
      "text": "Now there&#39;s nothing remarkable in this"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 271910.0,
      "end_time": 273503.0,
      "text": "until you learn that the center oat that it started from"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 273503.0,
      "end_time": 275517.0,
      "text": "represents the city of Tokyo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 275517.0,
      "end_time": 279582.0,
      "text": "and the surrounding oats are suburban railway stations."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 279583.0,
      "end_time": 282640.0,
      "text": "The slime mold had replicated"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 282640.0,
      "end_time": 284480.0,
      "text": "the Tokyo transport network"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 284480.0,
      "end_time": 286135.0,
      "text": "— (Laughter) —"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 286135.0,
      "end_time": 289130.0,
      "text": "a complex system developed over time"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 289130.0,
      "end_time": 293300.0,
      "text": "by community dwellings, civil engineering, urban planning."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 293300.0,
      "end_time": 295303.0,
      "text": "What had taken us well over 100 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 295303.0,
      "end_time": 298469.0,
      "text": "took the slime mold just over a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 298469.0,
      "end_time": 300122.0,
      "text": "The conclusion from their experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 300122.0,
      "end_time": 302632.0,
      "text": "was that the slime mold can form efficient networks"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 302632.0,
      "end_time": 305255.0,
      "text": "and solve the traveling salesman problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 305255.0,
      "end_time": 307519.0,
      "text": "It is a biological computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 307519.0,
      "end_time": 310143.0,
      "text": "As such, it has been mathematically modeled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 310143.0,
      "end_time": 311804.0,
      "text": "algorithmically analyzed."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 311804.0,
      "end_time": 314508.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been sonified, replicated, simulated."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 314509.0,
      "end_time": 317479.0,
      "text": "World over, teams of researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 317479.0,
      "end_time": 320449.0,
      "text": "are decoding its biological principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 320449.0,
      "end_time": 322590.0,
      "text": "to understand its computational rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 322590.0,
      "end_time": 324844.0,
      "text": "and applying that learning to the fields of electronics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 324844.0,
      "end_time": 327800.0,
      "text": "programming and robotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 327800.0,
      "end_time": 329234.0,
      "text": "So the question is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 329234.0,
      "end_time": 331253.0,
      "text": "how does this thing work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 331254.0,
      "end_time": 333414.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have a central nervous system."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 333414.0,
      "end_time": 335111.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have a brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 335112.0,
      "end_time": 336940.0,
      "text": "yet it can perform behaviors"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 336940.0,
      "end_time": 338928.0,
      "text": "that we associate with brain function."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 338928.0,
      "end_time": 340836.0,
      "text": "It can learn, it can remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 340836.0,
      "end_time": 343593.0,
      "text": "it can solve problems, it can make decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 343593.0,
      "end_time": 346308.0,
      "text": "So where does that intelligence lie?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 346308.0,
      "end_time": 348800.0,
      "text": "So this is a microscopy, a video I shot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 348800.0,
      "end_time": 351453.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s about 100 times magnification,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 351453.0,
      "end_time": 354320.0,
      "text": "sped up about 20 times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 354320.0,
      "end_time": 356106.0,
      "text": "and inside the slime mold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 356106.0,
      "end_time": 359548.0,
      "text": "there is a rhythmic pulsing flow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 359548.0,
      "end_time": 361716.0,
      "text": "a vein-like structure carrying"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 361716.0,
      "end_time": 365488.0,
      "text": "cellular material, nutrients and chemical information"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 365488.0,
      "end_time": 367346.0,
      "text": "through the cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 367346.0,
      "end_time": 370964.0,
      "text": "streaming first in one direction and then back in another."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 370964.0,
      "end_time": 374781.0,
      "text": "And it is this continuous, synchronous oscillation"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 374781.0,
      "end_time": 377370.0,
      "text": "within the cell that allows it to form"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 377370.0,
      "end_time": 380190.0,
      "text": "quite a complex understanding of its environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 380190.0,
      "end_time": 383388.0,
      "text": "but without any large-scale control center."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 383388.0,
      "end_time": 385969.0,
      "text": "This is where its intelligence lies."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 385969.0,
      "end_time": 389213.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not just academic researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 389213.0,
      "end_time": 391857.0,
      "text": "in universities that are interested in this organism."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 391857.0,
      "end_time": 394730.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, I set up SliMoCo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 394730.0,
      "end_time": 397700.0,
      "text": "the Slime Mould Collective."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 397700.0,
      "end_time": 400293.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an online, open, democratic network"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 400293.0,
      "end_time": 402389.0,
      "text": "for slime mold researchers and enthusiasts"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 402389.0,
      "end_time": 405118.0,
      "text": "to share knowledge and experimentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 405118.0,
      "end_time": 408860.0,
      "text": "across disciplinary divides"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 408860.0,
      "end_time": 411781.0,
      "text": "and across academic divides."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 411781.0,
      "end_time": 415221.0,
      "text": "The Slime Mould Collective membership is self-selecting."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 415221.0,
      "end_time": 418170.0,
      "text": "People have found the collective"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 418170.0,
      "end_time": 421715.0,
      "text": "as the slime mold finds the oats."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 421715.0,
      "end_time": 423407.0,
      "text": "And it comprises of scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 423408.0,
      "end_time": 424967.0,
      "text": "and computer scientists and researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 424967.0,
      "end_time": 427253.0,
      "text": "but also artists like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 427254.0,
      "end_time": 432346.0,
      "text": "architects, designers, writers, activists, you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 432346.0,
      "end_time": 436529.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very interesting, eclectic membership."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 436529.0,
      "end_time": 437866.0,
      "text": "Just a few examples:"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 437866.0,
      "end_time": 440991.0,
      "text": "an artist who paints with fluorescent Physarum;"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 440991.0,
      "end_time": 442563.0,
      "text": "a collaborative team"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 442563.0,
      "end_time": 446341.0,
      "text": "who are combining biological and electronic design"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 446341.0,
      "end_time": 449486.0,
      "text": "with 3D printing technologies in a workshop;"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 449486.0,
      "end_time": 451620.0,
      "text": "another artist who is using the slime mold"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 451620.0,
      "end_time": 453720.0,
      "text": "as a way of engaging a community"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 453720.0,
      "end_time": 456724.0,
      "text": "to map their area."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 456724.0,
      "end_time": 458885.0,
      "text": "Here, the slime mold is being used directly"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 458886.0,
      "end_time": 461764.0,
      "text": "as a biological tool, but metaphorically"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 461764.0,
      "end_time": 463748.0,
      "text": "as a symbol for ways of talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 463748.0,
      "end_time": 467602.0,
      "text": "about social cohesion, communication"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 467602.0,
      "end_time": 469465.0,
      "text": "and cooperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 469466.0,
      "end_time": 471976.0,
      "text": "Other public engagement activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 471976.0,
      "end_time": 473994.0,
      "text": "I run lots of slime mold workshops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 473994.0,
      "end_time": 476456.0,
      "text": "a creative way of engaging with the organism."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 476456.0,
      "end_time": 478140.0,
      "text": "So people are invited to come and learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 478140.0,
      "end_time": 480360.0,
      "text": "about what amazing things it can do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 480360.0,
      "end_time": 482682.0,
      "text": "and they design their own petri dish experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 482682.0,
      "end_time": 484998.0,
      "text": "an environment for the slime mold to navigate"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 484998.0,
      "end_time": 486635.0,
      "text": "so they can test its properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 486636.0,
      "end_time": 489800.0,
      "text": "Everybody takes home a new pet"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 489800.0,
      "end_time": 492200.0,
      "text": "and is invited to post their results"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 492200.0,
      "end_time": 494438.0,
      "text": "on the Slime Mould Collective."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 494438.0,
      "end_time": 495885.0,
      "text": "And the collective has enabled me"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 495886.0,
      "end_time": 498248.0,
      "text": "to form collaborations"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 498248.0,
      "end_time": 500841.0,
      "text": "with a whole array of interesting people."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 500841.0,
      "end_time": 502434.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been working with filmmakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 502434.0,
      "end_time": 505900.0,
      "text": "on a feature-length slime mold documentary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 505900.0,
      "end_time": 508558.0,
      "text": "and I stress feature-length,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 508558.0,
      "end_time": 510267.0,
      "text": "which is in the final stages of edit"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 510267.0,
      "end_time": 513293.0,
      "text": "and will be hitting your cinema screens very soon."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 513293.0,
      "end_time": 514773.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 514773.0,
      "end_time": 518108.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also enabled me to conduct what I think is"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 518107.0,
      "end_time": 520981.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s first human slime mold experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 520981.0,
      "end_time": 523953.0,
      "text": "This is part of an exhibition in Rotterdam last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 523953.0,
      "end_time": 528644.0,
      "text": "We invited people to become slime mold for half an hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 528644.0,
      "end_time": 531985.0,
      "text": "So we essentially tied people together"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 531985.0,
      "end_time": 534309.0,
      "text": "so they were a giant cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 534309.0,
      "end_time": 537153.0,
      "text": "and invited them to follow slime mold rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 537153.0,
      "end_time": 540584.0,
      "text": "You have to communicate through oscillations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 540584.0,
      "end_time": 541880.0,
      "text": "no speaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 541880.0,
      "end_time": 546813.0,
      "text": "You have to operate as one entity, one mass cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 546813.0,
      "end_time": 548396.0,
      "text": "no egos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 548397.0,
      "end_time": 550982.0,
      "text": "and the motivation for moving"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 550982.0,
      "end_time": 552890.0,
      "text": "and then exploring the environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 552890.0,
      "end_time": 554789.0,
      "text": "is in search of food."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 554789.0,
      "end_time": 558420.0,
      "text": "So a chaotic shuffle ensued as this bunch of strangers"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 558420.0,
      "end_time": 562328.0,
      "text": "tied together with yellow ropes wearing \"Being Slime Mold\" t-shirts"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 562328.0,
      "end_time": 565284.0,
      "text": "wandered through the museum park."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 565284.0,
      "end_time": 568610.0,
      "text": "When they met trees, they had to reshape"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 568610.0,
      "end_time": 571742.0,
      "text": "their connections and reform as a mass cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 571742.0,
      "end_time": 575728.0,
      "text": "through not speaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 575729.0,
      "end_time": 579870.0,
      "text": "This is a ludicrous experiment in many, many ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 579870.0,
      "end_time": 581360.0,
      "text": "This isn&#39;t hypothesis-driven."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 581360.0,
      "end_time": 583478.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not trying to prove, demonstrate anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 583479.0,
      "end_time": 585613.0,
      "text": "But what it did provide us was a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 585613.0,
      "end_time": 587961.0,
      "text": "of engaging a broad section of the public"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 587961.0,
      "end_time": 592392.0,
      "text": "with ideas of intelligence, agency, autonomy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 592392.0,
      "end_time": 594721.0,
      "text": "and provide a playful platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 594721.0,
      "end_time": 598453.0,
      "text": "for discussions about"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 598453.0,
      "end_time": 600837.0,
      "text": "the things that ensued."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 600837.0,
      "end_time": 603170.0,
      "text": "One of the most exciting things"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 603170.0,
      "end_time": 606300.0,
      "text": "about this experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 606300.0,
      "end_time": 608217.0,
      "text": "was the conversation that happened afterwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 608217.0,
      "end_time": 612400.0,
      "text": "An entirely spontaneous symposium happened in the park."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 612400.0,
      "end_time": 614690.0,
      "text": "People talked about the human psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 614690.0,
      "end_time": 615726.0,
      "text": "of how difficult it was to let go"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 615726.0,
      "end_time": 619350.0,
      "text": "of their individual personalities and egos."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 619350.0,
      "end_time": 622218.0,
      "text": "Other people talked about bacterial communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 622218.0,
      "end_time": 624197.0,
      "text": "Each person brought in their own"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 624197.0,
      "end_time": 627540.0,
      "text": "individual interpretation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 627540.0,
      "end_time": 628959.0,
      "text": "and our conclusion from this experiment was that"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 628959.0,
      "end_time": 632864.0,
      "text": "the people of Rotterdam were highly cooperative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 632865.0,
      "end_time": 635661.0,
      "text": "especially when given beer."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 635661.0,
      "end_time": 637627.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t just give them oats."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 637627.0,
      "end_time": 639189.0,
      "text": "We gave them beer as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 639189.0,
      "end_time": 641382.0,
      "text": "But they weren&#39;t as efficient as the slime mold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 641383.0,
      "end_time": 643367.0,
      "text": "and the slime mold, for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 643367.0,
      "end_time": 645736.0,
      "text": "is a fascinating subject matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 645736.0,
      "end_time": 647593.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s biologically fascinating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 647593.0,
      "end_time": 649176.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s computationally interesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 649177.0,
      "end_time": 651251.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also a symbol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 651251.0,
      "end_time": 654909.0,
      "text": "a way of engaging with ideas of community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 654909.0,
      "end_time": 658563.0,
      "text": "collective behavior, cooperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 658563.0,
      "end_time": 660689.0,
      "text": "A lot of my work draws on the scientific research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 660689.0,
      "end_time": 663872.0,
      "text": "so this pays homage to the maze experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 663873.0,
      "end_time": 665455.0,
      "text": "but in a different way."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 665455.0,
      "end_time": 667813.0,
      "text": "And the slime mold is also my working material."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 667813.0,
      "end_time": 673300.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a coproducer of photographs, prints, animations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 673300.0,
      "end_time": 674629.0,
      "text": "participatory events."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 674629.0,
      "end_time": 676977.0,
      "text": "Whilst the slime mold doesn&#39;t choose"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 676977.0,
      "end_time": 678882.0,
      "text": "to work with me, exactly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 678883.0,
      "end_time": 681485.0,
      "text": "it is a collaboration of sorts."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 681485.0,
      "end_time": 683577.0,
      "text": "I can predict certain behaviors"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 683577.0,
      "end_time": 685633.0,
      "text": "by understanding how it operates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 685633.0,
      "end_time": 687363.0,
      "text": "but I can&#39;t control it."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 687363.0,
      "end_time": 688947.0,
      "text": "The slime mold has the final say"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 688947.0,
      "end_time": 691780.0,
      "text": "in the creative process."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 691780.0,
      "end_time": 694567.0,
      "text": "And after all, it has its own internal aesthetics."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 694567.0,
      "end_time": 696371.0,
      "text": "These branching patterns that we see"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 696371.0,
      "end_time": 698920.0,
      "text": "we see across all forms, scales of nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 698921.0,
      "end_time": 701721.0,
      "text": "from river deltas to lightning strikes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 701721.0,
      "end_time": 705757.0,
      "text": "from our own blood vessels to neural networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 705757.0,
      "end_time": 708219.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s clearly significant rules at play"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 708220.0,
      "end_time": 710485.0,
      "text": "in this simple yet complex organism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 710485.0,
      "end_time": 714277.0,
      "text": "and no matter what our disciplinary perspective or our mode of inquiry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 714277.0,
      "end_time": 716600.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a great deal that we can learn"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 716600.0,
      "end_time": 717829.0,
      "text": "from observing and engaging"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 717829.0,
      "end_time": 720949.0,
      "text": "with this beautiful, brainless blob."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
